{"TopicId":177994,"ForumId":147,"TopicTitle":"Threads of the Month: September!","CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-01T20:51:40Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-01T20:51:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00221u4qhl1.png?1\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022155\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/1u4qhl1.png?1\u0022 width=\u0022174\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHappy September, everyone, and welcome to the latest installment of the Threads of the Month! Since it\u0027s going to be Fall, it\u0027s important that we all remember that orbit isn\u0027t flying, it\u0027s just \u003Cem\u003Efalling\u003C/em\u003E with style!\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E \u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHelping the moderators choose the threads this month are \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/89014-adsii1970/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002289014\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/89014-adsii1970/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@adsii1970\u003C/a\u003E, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/172792-benjamin-kerman/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022172792\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/172792-benjamin-kerman/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Benjamin Kerman\u003C/a\u003E, and \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/38787-klond/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002238787\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/38787-klond/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@klond\u003C/a\u003E. Thank you for bringing our attention to some excellent threads. If you\u0027d like to nominate a thread to be a TOTM, please hit the report button in the top right, and add a comment like \u0022TOTM.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow, on to the show!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFirst up to the plate is something straight out of a Hollywood movie. KSP doesn\u0027t have animals, but \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/162839-epicspacetroll139/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022162839\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/162839-epicspacetroll139/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@EpicSpaceTroll139\u003C/a\u003E proves that \u003Ca href=\u0022https://youtu.be/dMjQ3hA9mEA\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Elife, uh, finds a way\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed9687955861\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/177407-dinosaur-emporium/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:226px;max-width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRemember how Bruce Willis became an astronaut? Or how the debris field was in a retrograde orbit in \u003Cem\u003EGravity\u003C/em\u003E? Or how asteroids in the asteroid belt are touching each other? Or how... well, you get the picture. \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/81207-peadar1987/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002281207\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/81207-peadar1987/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@peadar1987\u003C/a\u003E has collected all of these goofs, gaffes, and dopey devices in to one thread for your enjoyment. Reader beware!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed2593548431\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/170269-bad-science-in-fiction-hall-of-shame/\u0026amp;\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:226px;max-width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m pretty much stuck.\u003Cbr\u003E\nThat\u0027s my considered opinion.\u003Cbr\u003E\nStuck.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd now, with \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/137508-mikki/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022137508\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/137508-mikki/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Mikki\u003C/a\u003E\u0027s \u003Cu\u003EThe Martian\u003C/u\u003E-inspired mission, you can be stuck, too!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed6960555696\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/174398-the-dunatian-24/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:226px;max-width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere\u0027s a fun fact: the new Canadian five dollar bill was unveiled by astronaut Chris Hadfield when he was onboard the ISS as commander. Here\u0027s another fun fact: Chris Hadfied installed the Canadarm2 on the ISS, which is featured on the back of the bill! Why do I mention this? Because \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/161599-maiantrey/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022161599\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/161599-maiantrey/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@MaianTrey\u003C/a\u003E is building a \u003Cstrong\u003Estock\u003C/strong\u003E ISS with a \u003Cstrong\u003Estock\u003C/strong\u003E shuttle and a \u003Cstrong\u003Estock \u003C/strong\u003ECanadarm! Wowee! \u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed7912238647\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/176236-maians-stock-iss-replica-videos-through-sts-92/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:226px;max-width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen I first started playing KSP, I was drawn to the cartoon Kerbals and the derpy explosions. As my playing time progressed, however, I discovered the wonder of physics, the lure of distant planets, the mesmerizing possibilities the game has to offer. But the possibilities that real life has to offer make a simple video game pale in compassion. I\u0027m sure that many kids have been inspired by \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/4-harvester/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u00224\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/4-harvester/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@HarvesteR\u003C/a\u003E\u0027s pet project, and this month I\u0027d like to shine the spotlight on \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/131541-ptrevtrevs/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022131541\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/131541-ptrevtrevs/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@pTrevTrevs\u003C/a\u003E, who posted his own inspirational story.\u00A0 He\u0027s chasing his dream as an aerospace engineer.\u00A0 Best wishes, and good luck!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed6459476849\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/177459-an-expression-of-gratitude/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:226px;max-width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs always, the TOTM images were made by \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/89014-adsii1970/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002289014\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/89014-adsii1970/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@adsii1970\u003C/a\u003E. A big thank you for his help here. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EThat\u0027s all for this month, folks\u003C/span\u003E! Have a great month!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Just Jim","CreatedById":148725,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-01T21:38:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGreat choices! Congrats everyone!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFYI... I\u0027m a really big fan of the \u003Cem\u003E\u0022Bad Science in Fiction Hall of Shame\u0022\u00A0\u003C/em\u003EGlad to see it (and all the rest) getting some love!!!\u00A0\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-09-01T21:38:42Z\u0022 title=\u002209/01/2018 09:38  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 1, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Just Jim\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pTrevTrevs","CreatedById":131541,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-01T22:44:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh wow, didn\u0027t expect that!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"EpicSpaceTroll139","CreatedById":162839,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-02T01:50:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWow! I never thought I would make it on here! Thanks everyone!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI will bring more dinosaurs as soon as I sort out my problematic computer.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mikki","CreatedById":137508,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-02T06:40:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAAAHHHH! Again! I never thought this would become such an successfull mission, nearly 2000 people have allready downloaded this from STEAM...\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnd i am glad to see rather few rants about\u00A0Bob\u0060s severe stuckness on Dunas Acidalia Planitia...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MaianTrey","CreatedById":161599,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-03T12:14:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh dang, I\u0027m in here? Thank you very much for the mention! I\u0027ve had a busy week, but the ISS is still progressing, so more videos to come soon.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbinchaser","CreatedById":160817,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-07T05:34:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy goal is to eventually get one of my stories on here. Congratulations to all the OPs.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HansonKerman","CreatedById":185809,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-09-08T21:27:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223443612\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022177994\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221535835100\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022123837\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Dman979\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 9/1/2018 at 4:51 PM, Dman979 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nH\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003Eappy\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E September, everyone, and welcome to the latest installment of the Threads of the Month!\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E \u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Lucida Sans Unicode\u0027, \u0027Lucida Grande\u0027, sans-serif;\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E I read \u201C\u003Cem\u003Elast\u003C/em\u003E\u201D \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:\u0027Lucida Sans Unicode\u0027, \u0027Lucida Grande\u0027, sans-serif;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EI freak\u00E9d out.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}